title: Unable to start queues for ranked in EUNE
body: First, i was in a lobby, then someone picked and it froze at 0 secs, it froze for everybody in the lobby, and everyone left, I am not sure whether i lost LP for leaving or not, since everybody left already, now to the real problem, I am unable to play ranked, whenever i try to search for a ranked match, the button goes gray, and the X button to cancel doesn't work, however, I am still able to check the profile, collection and such things, and I have to close every task for the client through task manager, and the problem will still occur if I relaunch the client..

replies.body: Were you able to try and queue for any other game modes and you couldn't or was ranked the only queue affected? If no other queues would work either, your network might have hit some kind of hiccup along the way to our servers and wasn't able to get a clear signal anymore. Do a quick trace route to our EU servers at 31.186.224.42 using [WinMTR](http://winmtr.net/winmtr-v0-92-now-available/) and post what kind of results you get here.

Now it's working, although I had good internet connection, every time i relaunched the launcher it said it was restoring the launcher to previous version, and no, I didn't try other gamemodes, anyway, as it's working well now you don't have to worry, thanks for the reply.
